  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the present experiment is to examine oxytocin's behavioral and neural effects on
      social pain empathy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In the current study, the investigators plan to examine whether oxytocin modulates behavior
      and neural activity during observing another person being excluded in an online ball-tossing
      game (a modified cyberball paradigm).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
